Sir Lord Jimmy Crystal.

280
00:33:59,455 --> 00:34:01,498
"Tu seras mon bras droit,

281
00:34:01,665 --> 00:34:02,958
"un bras puissant,

282
00:34:03,292 --> 00:34:05,377
