357
00:42:45,897 --> 00:42:46,940
Elle.

358
00:42:50,360 --> 00:42:51,903
Je la choisis, elle.

359
00:43:14,175 --> 00:43:15,218
Père,

360
00:43:16,761 --> 00:43:17,846
