377
00:45:05,870 --> 00:45:07,455
Bonne nuit, les Télétubbies.

378
00:45:08,206 --> 00:45:09,374
Dipsy, Laa-Laa !

379
00:45:09,541 --> 00:45:10,708
Tête de gland !

380
00:45:11,334 --> 00:45:12,961
